@pkpp1233 @kokozaurz @PatrickGuo

Ok, the problem is that a recent global renaming for Tensorflow to TensorFlow caught the native identifier in tensorflow_jni.h but did not correspondingly rename TensorflowClassifier.java.

Either s/TensorFlow/Tensorflow/ in tensorflow_jni.h, or rename and change the class of TensorflowClassifier.java to TensorFlowClassifier. I'll submit a fix to do the latter soon.
